A bright, high-energy comedic commercial for a distraction-free lifestyle product. Fast cuts, upbeat quirky music, bold sound effects.

• A businessman slams his “phone” on a meeting table—his hand makes a sad little pat.
• A guy at the gym tries to watch a workout video on invisible air and nods like it’s so inspiring.
• A woman on a date pretends to text her friend under the table, but she’s literally typing into emptiness.
• A kid plays a mobile game by furiously tapping thin air—victory fanfare plays anyway.
Cut to super-fast graphics:
“Less distraction.”
“More focus.”
“More… nothing.”
Wide shot: everyone in a park doing their usual phone motions—but every hand is empty, like a synchronized dance of imaginary devices.
Final VO, comedic but smooth:
“The future of nothing in your hand. NoPhone.”
